10.10	Slashed	Slashed	Slashed is a low budget independent horror film, financed and directed by Ash and written by Jed Shepherd. The film was shot in 2002, purely on a video camcorder when Ash were on tour in the United States supporting Coldplay - who subsequently appeared in the movie as detectives, along with various other musicians who the band ran into on their tour, including Dave Grohl, Moby and Neil Hannon.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/James_Nesbitt_July_2008.jpg/120px-James_Nesbitt_July_2008.jpg
